columns.name: network_acl_id
columns.description: The ID of the network ACL.

columns.name: arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) specifying the network ACL.

columns.name: is_default
columns.description: Indicates whether this is the default network ACL for the VPC.

columns.name: vpc_id
columns.description: The ID of the VPC for the network ACL.

columns.name: owner_id
columns.description: The ID of the AWS account that owns the network ACL.

columns.name: associations
columns.description: Any associations between the network ACL and one or more subnets.

columns.name: entries
columns.description: One or more entries (rules) in the network ACL.

columns.name: tags_src
columns.description: A list of tags that are attached to Network ACL.
